{"tid":2371829,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"濕疹｜新引入非類固醇藥膏安全性高最啱臉皮薄位置","createTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T07:21:11.000Z","uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2994ebb016354a40e6e717f2de7697280f0cd212","tid":2371829,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"濕疹｜醫生解構類固醇藥膏治濕疹注意事項 新引入非類固醇藥膏安全性高最啱臉皮薄位置<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210108/FMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2FFMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=587f87f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2FFMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU%2F&h=7e9e288e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210108/FMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，醫學界去年引入了名為PDE4抑制劑的非類固醇藥膏，原理是透過抑制皮膚細胞中過度活躍的PDE4酵素，從而達到紓緩濕疹的發炎與痕癢。胡惠福醫生解釋，外用的PDE4抑制劑不含類固醇，安全性相對較高，患者可長期使用，同時適用於眼皮、臉部及頸部等皮膚較薄位置。根據使用指引，外用PDE4抑制劑的適用年齡為兩歲或以上，適用於輕微至中度嚴重濕疹，使用前建議先諮詢醫生意見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人試過？"},{"pid":"7905c6234580525660c716ef42108c6d4d6015ef","tid":2371829,"uid":78087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2994ebb016354a40e6e717f2de7697280f0cd212","tid":2371829,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"濕疹｜醫生解構類固醇藥膏治濕疹注意事項 新引入非類固醇藥膏安全性高最啱臉皮薄位置<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210108/FMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2FFMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=587f87f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210108%2FFMWDZFXC3NBRHC22DJVPXBYTZU%2F&h=7e9e288e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/